28:47.923 --> 28:56.153
worked on. I'd rather do that than anything I can 
think of. Oh, okay. And I know this is a naive

28:59.759 --> 29:04.988
question, but what's the first thing you begin to 
look for when you start to design it? Do you say,

29:05.489 --> 29:07.974
what's the biggest thing I can get for the money? 
